data.description: Nestled in the desirable Panorama Park Estates neighborhood, this spacious home offers a versatile layout totaling 6 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms plus a bonus room for potential home office, game room with a built in bar providing ample living space! Enjoy breathtaking Mountain and Territorial views from the expansive deck, which boasts a built-in hot tub for year-round relaxation. Inside you'll find a great sized kitchen, roomy living and family room, and a private suite in the primary bedroom!
